headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires B&W Insurance Agency, Inc.
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Washington, Pennsylvania-based B&W Insurance Agency, Inc. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
